efining the structure of the matrix. In this paper we\nextensively examine the case of real matrices but we also consider pattern\nstructures. As far as we know there do not exist methods in the literature able\nto compute such distance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2014 14:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
